OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cloudy but mostly dry start
OL,6,Fbecoming brighter with showers
OL,7,Fbuilding from the late morning. These
OL,8,Fshowers will become slow moving and
OL,9,Fheavy in the afternoon.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FBright spells and showers,
OL,12,Fsome heavy, during the evening. Clear
OL,13,Fspells increase as showers die from
OL,14,Flate evening but cloud and rain spread
OL,15,Fnortheast later.
OL,16,
OL,17,CFriday:FEarly cloud and rain soon
OL,18,Fclear northeast to leave the morning
OL,19,Fdry with sunny spells. The odd shower
OL,20,Fwill develop during the afternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
