OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FDry at
OL,6,Ffirst, cloud, rain soon push northeast
OL,7,FSaturday. Becoming dry north as rain
OL,8,Fbecomes heavy in the south Sunday.
OL,9,FRain passes northeast Monday morning,
OL,10,Fbecoming drier in the afternoon.
